Interface SecuredStatement

  • All Superinterfaces:
    FrontsTriple, SecuredItem, Statement
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SecuredStatementImpl

    public interface SecuredStatement
extends Statement, SecuredItem
    The interface for secured Statement instances. Use the SecuredStatement.Factory to create instances
